                                                                                                               the characteristics of the flaw, and provide any suggestions for the
                                                                                                               manufacturer to consider when determining how to fix the software flaw.
                                                                                                            b. Providing instructions for the IoT device customer to use to send the
                                                                                                               manufacturer software flaw reports.
                                                                                                            c. Providing a description of the procedures the manufacturer follows for
                                                                                                               processing the software flaw reports, determining which flaws need to be
                                                                                                               fixed, for scheduling corrections to identified flaws, and for how the
                                                                                                               manufacturer will notify the IoT customer of the status of the software flaw
